description: Beneath a vaulted ceiling, a pearl-handled filigreed mandolin hangs on one of the smooth granite walls.  A gilded maple table and an oval-shaped speckled marble counter sit in opposite corners while a pile of striped throw pillows rests on a polished oak floor.
